&lt;p&gt;The following proposes a strategy using a Mealy Deterministic Finite State Machine (DFSM) that switches between five states with two different algorithms. The Rebound avoider/follower strategy through proximity sensors, and the search blob/ePuck approach using the 2D image processing of the ePuck embedded camera. Simulation is implemented on &lt;a href="https://www.coppeliarobotics.com/downloads"&gt;V-rep ProEdu v3.6&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

